		&nbsp;<a href="pop_profile.asp?mode=display&amp;id=6142"><img src="icon_profile.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Show Profile" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>
        
			&nbsp;<a href="JavaScript:openWindow('pop_mail.asp?id=6142')"><img src="icon_email.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Email Poster" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        &nbsp;<a href="post.asp?method=ReplyQuote&amp;REPLY_ID=56798&amp;TOPIC_ID=6835&amp;FORUM_ID=2&amp;CAT_ID=1&amp;Forum_Title=General+Discussions&amp;Topic_Title=Terrorclaws+or+shawl+quest%3F&amp;M="><img src="icon_reply_topic.gif" height="15" width="15" alt="Reply with Quote" border="0" align="absmiddle" hspace="6"></a>

        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         When I went home for lunch from work I decided to run an experiment because this all sparked my interest.  Wanted to find out how much Gem encrusted ring actually saved me per cast.</P><P>I got full mana then chained Funeral Pyre till I got insuffecient message. Did this twice with ring and twice without. Here are the results:</P><P>With Ring <BR>First time 10 casts 9% Left on bar. (100%-9%= 91%/10 = 9.1% of my mana per casting). <BR>Second time 10 casts 12% left on bar (100%-12 = 88%/10 = 8.8% of my mana per casting). <BR>Average of 9.1% and 8.8% per casting is 8.95% of my mana per cast. According to this -><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=225999" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=225999</a>I have 3353 mana<BR>So 3353 x .0895 = 300 mana per casting with ring.</P><P>Without ring<BR>first time 9 casts 5% remaining (100%-5%=95%/9 = 10.6% per casting<BR>second time 8 casts 13% remaining (100%-13% = 87%/8 = 10.9% per cast<BR>Average of 10.75% of my mana per cast<BR>3353 x .1075 = 360 mana per casting without ring</P><P>So I figure I am saving roughly (60/360) = 17% on mana costs with ring<BR>And 150/450 = 33% saved total including scm3, ring, and specialization</P><P>It isnt earthshaking but it adds up and helps.../shrug</P><P><BR><img src="http://ourworld.cs.com/bgrmail/zorlak.jpg" border=0></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
      </tr>

